      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,9 @@\n+This release improves the readability of configuration override log messages by using relative paths and human-friendly formatting.\n+\n+## \ud83d\udc1e Bug fixes\n+\n+### Improved config override log readability\n+\n+Configuration override log messages now use relative paths and human-friendly formatting instead of absolute paths and raw Python repr output, making debug output easier to read.\n+\n+*By @mavam and @claude in #19.*"
